Title: Relates to procedures for certain temporary custody orders
Summary: Establishes procedures for temporary custody orders that include a rebuttable presumption that the parents or a person acting as a parent shall have temporary joint legal and shared physical custody and shall share equal parenting time.

ActClause: AN ACT to amend the domestic relations law, in relation to procedures for certain temporary custody orders
